{"tid":1575100,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[收集文宣] 長期集中 造低美心  九月之星 吉野家","createTime":"2019-09-16T16:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T02:55:27.000Z","uid":137789,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd803ce887a8d347e19d6a792de2b3f5e7228724","tid":1575100,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"目標係令最多人一齊參與，人少，任你罷幾大個list都冇用，人夠多，一齊做，一間就夠，死得一間就死得第二間，做呢啲嘢只有夠人多一齊做先有效，集中一間，就算係美心都一樣死<br />\n<br />\n睇大家有幾齊心，我當就揀咗美心，咁大家一齊推文宣，要全港都知，美心全封殺集中推到佢清盤<br />\n<br />\n有遊戲玩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXY7O8Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXY7O8Q.jpg&h=2f0f103c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個list，試下圖像化，每間出埋logo/招牌/門面<br />\n玩咩？玩尋找美心的故事<br />\n<br />\n叫大家經過List中嘅鋪影相打卡，話俾人知「呢間就係美心集團嘅，睇佢幾時執」<br />\n<br />\n個個都咁玩，好快大家對佢個list啲名都琅琅上口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長期集中<br />\n造低美心<br />\n<br />\n九月之星<br />\n吉野家<br />\n<br />\n開唔開心<br />\n興唔興奮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n九月之星 吉野家 文宣點搞好？玩返獅子狗？"},{"pid":"397a6b5da7e842e19141a68d74a77148568596b2","tid":1575100,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期三有大綱睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%